(714) 957-4033). SCR's 11th annual production. Tue.-Fri., 7:30 p.m.; Sat., 2:30 
p.m.; Sun., noon and 4 p.m.; Dec. 18, 20, 2:30 p.m. Ends Dec. 23. $22-$24. 
</P>
<P>
