Caravan Theatre. Thur., 8 p.m.: El Camino College, Marsee Auditorium, 16007 
Crenshaw Blvd., Torrance, (213) 329-5345; $18-$25. Fri., 8 p.m.: Plummer 
Auditorium, 201 E. Chapman Ave., Fullerton, (714) 773-3371; $12.50-$17.50. Next 
